### Why

Harden the sotp CLI against data loss (silent field drops, abort-on-single-failure),
input validation gaps (unvalidated TrackId, limited PR body parsing), and accidental
test file deletion. Add automated spec.md verification (attribution and frontmatter)
and reinvention detection via canonical module rules.
